The Chronicle Bongani Ndlovu, Showbiz Correspondent Bulawayo Provincial Affairs and Devolution Minister Judith Ncube is expected to pay her last respects to the late artiste, rapper Calvin Nhliziyo at his Luveve 5 home. The minister will join other mourners in consoling the Nhliziyo family following his untimely death last Sunday. Cal Vin will be buried in Bulawayo on Sunday. more to follow… – @bonganinkunzi